                                <p class="mb-4 size-18">Our faculty and staff have achieved regional, national and international recognition for not only their artistry, but also for their commitment to the success of each of our students. Our international faculty represents seven countries and are outstanding educators, caring role models and successful worldwide performers, composers and musicologists.</p>
